{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/99106", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/99106/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/99106/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/99106/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/99106", "id": 1299852398, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M5Neixu", "number": 99106, "title": "Nested macros called with \"constant\" fragments can't capture said fragments as \"constant\"", "user": {"login": "MasterPtato", "id": 23087326, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIzMDg3MzI2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/23087326?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato", "html_url": "https://github.com/MasterPtato", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 132910982, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxMzI5MTA5ODI=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-macros", "name": "A-macros", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: All kinds of macros (custom derive, macro_rules!, proc macros, ..)"}, {"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 4, "created_at": "2022-07-10T07:36:52Z", "updated_at": "2022-07-22T06:52:13Z", "closed_at": "2022-07-22T06:51:25Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "### Context\r\nThis is a bug related to the unstable feature [macro metavariable expressions](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/83527).\r\n### Issue\r\nNested macros called with \"constant\" fragments from within another macro don't keep that \"constant\" status for the inner macro call.\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nmacro_rules! outer {\r\n    (0) => {\r\n        outer!(1)\r\n    };\r\n    ($lit:literal) => {\r\n        macro_rules! inner {\r\n            (1) => {\r\n                println!(\"constant fragment\")\r\n            };\r\n            ($$lit:literal) => {\r\n                println!(\"literal fragment\")\r\n            };\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        inner!($lit);\r\n        inner!(1);\r\n    };\r\n}\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    outer!(0);\r\n    inner!(1);\r\n}\r\n```\r\nWorking example: [Rust Playground](https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=nightly&mode=debug&edition=2021&gist=5a323561daf700bc2c00b3ba04334ac5)\r\n\r\n### Expected output\r\n```\r\nconstant fragment\r\nconstant fragment\r\nconstant fragment\r\n```\r\n### Actual output\r\n```\r\nliteral fragment\r\nconstant fragment\r\nconstant fragment\r\n```\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n> PS: The title and issue description are a bit hard to understand, clarity suggestions are appreciated.", "closed_by": {"login": "MasterPtato", "id": 23087326, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIzMDg3MzI2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/23087326?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato", "html_url": "https://github.com/MasterPtato", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MasterPtato/foll